# Mount against a wall face at -Z. Bracket at sz=0, torch body at sz=1.

# --- WALL BRACKET (Metal, at sz=0) ---
S 0 0 0  1 0 0  Metal
S 0 0 0  1 1 0  Metal

# --- TORCH SHAFT (Wood, at sz=1) ---
S 0 0 0  1 0 1  Wood
S 0 0 0  1 1 1  Wood

# --- FLAME (glow, top of torch) ---
S 0 0 0  1 2 1  glow
